# You-Sir Juan skills pack path

## Canonical paths

| Context | Path |
|---------|------|
| **ai-skills-library** (source of truth) | `skills/yousirjuan/<skill-id>/SKILL.md` |
| **This monorepo** (submodule) | `vendor/ai-skills-library/skills/yousirjuan/<skill-id>/SKILL.md` |
| **Cursor flat install** | `.cursor/skills/<skill-id>/SKILL.md` (symlink from install script) |

## Retired (never use)

- `skills/project/yousirjuan/`
- Frontmatter `domain: project/yousirjuan`

## Agent-managed

Edit platform skills only in **marvelousempire/ai-skills-library**, then bump this submodule. Do not copy skill bodies into `yousirjuan/` outside the vendor tree.

Applies to **Nephew**, **Bishop**, **Automata**, **Scene Skout**, and all Cursor/Claude agents on this repo.

Full rule: [`vendor/ai-skills-library/rules/library/yousirjuan-skills-pack-path/body.md`](../../vendor/ai-skills-library/rules/library/yousirjuan-skills-pack-path/body.md) (after submodule sync).

Install:

```bash
cd vendor/ai-skills-library && ./scripts/install-repo-skills-to-cursor-project.sh "$(cd ../.. && pwd)"
```
